OL,3,CBrewDog: A timeline of controversies
OL,4,Cas James Watt calls time as boss
OL,6,FBy James Hockaday, Multimedia Producer
OL,8,FBrewDog boss James Watt is to step
OL,9,Fdown as chief executive after 17 years
OL,10,Fat the helm, having seen the Scottish
OL,11,Fbrewer and pub chain grow into a
OL,12,Fglobal phenomenon.
OL,14,FMr Watt will hand over the reins to
OL,15,FChief Operating Officer James Arrow,
OL,16,Fbut will take on a newly-created non-
OL,17,Fexecutive role of "captain and co-
OL,18,Ffounder".
