OL,6,FHe will retain his 21% shareholding in
OL,7,Fthe firm, will remain a board member
OL,8,Fand a director, and will also be a
OL,9,Fpart-time strategic adviser to the
OL,10,Fbusiness.
OL,12,FThe "punk" craft beer brand is now
OL,13,Favailable in 57 countries, producing
OL,14,F367 million cans of beer and serving
OL,15,F16.7 million punters in its bars in
OL,16,F2023. It currently employs 2,530
OL,17,Fpeople across its head office, four
OL,18,Fbreweries and over 120 bars.
