OL,3,CBrewDog: A timeline of controversies
OL,4,Cas James Watt calls time as boss
OL,6,FIt's a far cry from when Mr Watt and
OL,7,Fco-founder Martin Dickie started their
OL,8,Fbusiness aged 24 from a garage in the
OL,9,Fnortheastern Scottish town of
OL,10,FFraserburgh ` selling hand-filled
OL,11,Fbottles out of a van at local markets.
OL,13,FHowever, this dizzying success hasn't
OL,14,Fcome without its criticism, including
OL,15,Fclaims of toxic workplace practices,
OL,16,Falleged inappropriate behaviour and
OL,17,Fmisleading advertising.
OL,19,FHere's a timeline of some of BrewDog's
OL,20,Fmain controversies.
