OL,6,F2017 - Legal battle over Elvis Juice
OL,8,FBrewDog faced a trademark dispute from
OL,9,Fthe Elvis Presley Estate over its
OL,10,FElvis Juice beer.
OL,12,FThe UK Intellectual Property Office
OL,13,F(UKIPO) initially ruled in favour of
OL,14,Fthe estate in June 2017, claiming the
OL,15,Fname could easily be seen as an
OL,16,Fendorsement by King of Rock 'n' Roll's
OL,17,Festate.
