OL,6,FBrewDog was forced to apologise after
OL,7,Fformer workers alleged a "culture of
OL,8,Ffear" within the business and "toxic
OL,9,Fattitudes" towards junior staff.JA
OL,10,F"significant number" of ex-employees
OL,11,Fwere said to have suffered "mental
OL,12,Fillness" as a result of working at
OL,13,Fbrewer, signatories to an open letter
OL,14,Fsaid.
