OL,3,CBrewDog: A timeline of controversies
OL,4,Cas James Watt calls time as boss
OL,6,FBrewDog was accused of being
OL,7,Fdisingenuous after launching an "anti-
OL,8,Fsponsor" campaign during the 2022 FIFA
OL,9,FWorld Cup in protest over host Qatar's
OL,10,Fhuman rights abuses.
OL,12,FThe brewer said it was making a
OL,13,Fstatement over the Gulf state's
OL,14,Fcriminalisation of homosexuality, use
OL,15,Fof corporal punishment and poor
OL,16,Ftreatment of migrant workers who
OL,17,Freportedly died during preparations
OL,18,Ffor the football tournament.
