OL,6,FIt put up billboards saying, "First
OL,7,FRussia, then Qatar, can't wait for
OL,8,FNorth Korea" and said that all profits
OL,9,Ffrom its Lost Lager sold during the
OL,10,Ftournament would go towards human
OL,11,Frights charities.
OL,13,FHowever, BrewDog raised eyebrows by
OL,14,Foffering a "fan zone" where punters
OL,15,Fcould watch the tournament matches.
