OL,10,Fas to why cans of BrewDog lager were
OL,11,Favailable to buy in Qatar.
OL,13,FBrewDog said it doesn't sell directly
OL,14,Fto the country, rather it works with a
OL,15,Fdistributor that sells to multiple
