OL,3,CBrewDog: A timeline of controversies
OL,4,Cas James Watt calls time as boss
OL,6,FMr Watt paid nearly #500,000 out of
OL,7,Fhis own pocket to unhappy customers
OL,8,Fwho felt duped by a bungled "solid
OL,9,Fgold" beer can promotion.
OL,11,FIn 2021 BrewDog told buyers they had a
OL,12,Fchance of finding a "solid gold" beer
OL,13,Fcan hidden inside some cases of beer.
OL,15,FHowever, some customers complained
OL,16,Fafter finding out their beer cans were
OL,17,Fmerely gold plated, rather than made
OL,18,Fentirely of gold.
