OL,3,CBrewDog: A timeline of controversies
OL,4,Cas James Watt calls time as boss
OL,6,FIn a LinkedIn post, Mr Watt accepted
OL,7,Ffault for the "#500,000 mistake",
OL,8,Fclaiming that "in his enthusiasm", he
OL,9,F"misunderstood the process of how they
OL,10,Fwere made and the initial tweets I
OL,11,Fsent out told customers of the
OL,12,Fprospect of finding 'solid gold cans'".
OL,14,F"It was a silly mistake and it only
OL,15,Fappeared in around 3 of a total of 50
OL,16,Fposts about the promotion but as it
OL,17,Fturns out, those 3 tweets were enough
OL,18,Fto do a lot of damage."
