OL,6,FHe said the ASA had got involved and
OL,7,Fagreed that the promotion had been
OL,8,Fmisleading.
OL,10,FMr Watt added: "I got in touch with
OL,11,Fall 50 winners and let them know that
OL,12,Fif they were unhappy with their prize
OL,13,FI would personally offer them the full
OL,14,Fcash amount as an alternative.
OL,16,F"Furthermore, I promised to fund this
OL,17,Fmyself so the business did not have to
OL,18,Fsuffer financially from my mistake.
OL,19,FAll in all, it ended up costing me
OL,20,Faround #470,000 ` well over 2 and a
OL,21,Fhalf years 'salary'."
