OL,6,F2023 - Complaint over BrewDog 'carbon
OL,7,Fnegative' claims
OL,9,FThe ASA upheld a complaint against
OL,10,FBrewDog over "misleading" claims that
OL,11,Fits beers were "carbon negative".
OL,13,FIn an ad campaign launched in July,
OL,14,Fthe brand touted itself as the "the
OL,15,Fworld's first carbon negative
OL,16,Fbrewery", describing its products as
OL,17,F"beer for your grandchildren".
