OL,6,FWhile BrewDog has installed a number
OL,7,Fof , the ASA ruled that "no
OL,8,Finformation provided in the ad which
OL,9,Fexplained the basis of BrewDog's
OL,10,F'carbon negative' accreditation."
OL,12,FThe regulator added: "Although we
OL,13,Facknowledged that the ad referred
OL,14,Fconsumers to a link for the BrewDog
OL,15,Fwebsite which contained further
