OL,6,FIn a furious response on LinkedIn, Mr
OL,7,FWatt said the information supporting
OL,8,FBrewDog's carbon negative campaign is
OL,9,F"extensive" but that a slightly
OL,10,Fshorter explanation was needed due to
OL,11,FInstagram's formatting.JHe added: "Two
OL,12,Fpeople complained and the ASA upheld
