OL,6,F2024 - BrewDog under fire for dropping
OL,7,FLiving Wage pledge
OL,9,FBrewDog faced a challenge from
OL,10,Femployees at the start of this year
OL,11,Fafter announcing it would be hiring
OL,12,Fnew staff on the legal minimum wage
OL,13,Finstead of the higher voluntary rate.
OL,15,FThe Unite union criticised the move as
OL,16,F"outrageous", especially coming amid
OL,17,Fthe continuing cost-of-living crisis,
OL,18,Fpointing out that BrewDog had been
OL,19,Fpaying the real living wage since 2015.
