OL,6,FIn a letter to staff, the brewer said:
OL,7,F"Even with this strong performance
OL,8,Fover Christmas, as a wider business
OL,9,Fthere is no hiding from the fact that
OL,10,Fin 2023 we made a trading loss, and
OL,11,Fdespite many efforts in the past 12
OL,12,Fmonths to reduce our spending we still
OL,13,Fneed to find more ways to get this
OL,14,Fbusiness back to profitability and the
OL,15,Ffinancial stability that is needed.
OL,16,F"Inevitably, this does mean making
OL,17,Fsome hard decisions."
